flowchart TB
    Raw[CIC-IDS2017 CSV] --> Load[Load & Merge]
    Load --> Label[Multiclass + Binary Labels]
    Label --> Clean[Clean & Clip Outliers]
    Clean --> Feat[Feature Selection - 25 features]
    Feat --> Scale[StandardScaler]
    Scale --> Split[70/20/10 Stratified Split]
    Split --> Train[Train 4 Models]
    Train --> Compare[Compare]
    Compare --> Best[Select Best - XGBoost]
    Best --> Eval[Binary Eval on Simulation Set]
    Eval --> Deploy[Deploy in WAF]
